no-api-keys-description = API key jalqabaa uumuf, "Create API Credentials" cuqaasi; booda maqaa API Credentials kee kenni, akkasumas “Generate Credentials” cuqaasuun API Credentials adda ta’e uumi. Erga uumtee booda, secret key hatattamaan copy godhi, sababni isaa yeroo tokko qofa mul’ata.
